I"7<h1 id="about-the-journal">About the Journal</h1>

<p>Studium is the journal of confessional language studies at Martin Luther College.</p>

<p>Studium fosters the study of the confessional languages at Martin Luther College and in Wisconsin Evangelical Lutheran Synod by publishing original, English translations of historic Latin and German resources drawn from the Lutheran tradition in both Europe and the United States.</p>

<h2 id="history">History</h2>

<p>The preface to <a href="/issue/issue-19">Issue 19</a> includes a brief history of the publication.</p>
